Content: [dscrdeql] <stretcher83> iv recently quit smoking, like 12 months ago maybe a tad longer, i used to smoke a full 50 gram pouch of golden virginia in about 5 days and that went on for a good number of years, i was lucky enough to have a friend who was well in to vape pens, but not the little pen style ones, im talking about these big chonging sticks , cloud chasers they call them, sub ohm. anyway he talked me into giving it a go one day but you dont smoke it like a normal ciggarett , you have to take a big full lung inhale of the thing and so ik did, oh my god it felt so uncomfertable i couldnt understand how he could vape it like that, but after a few days i tried it again but i kept vaping it all day, the uncomfertablness  subsided after a good 10 - 15 goes of it, iv not gone back to the cancer sticks , yet. after about 2 months on the vape mod i bought , i waqs in work and a local vape shops warehouse was moving to a diffrent building in a different town , and the fella that ran the building with all the vape liquid stock in asked me if i wanted any free liquids, i was like err yeh , whats the catch, he said because the law had recently changed in the eu/uk , shops where no longer allowed to sell bottles of e liquids bigger than 10ml if it had nicotine in them, so he had loads of previous stock that was 60ml bottle size and had max 6mg nicotine in them, they was good quality american made e liquids so i was like ok how much can i have, he said as much as you want, i took 3 big pallets full of mixed 30ml bottles, and 60 ml bottles , some was 3mg nicotine some was 6 mg nicotine, and i also got a few boxes of 0 mg nicotine, 6000 bottles i got,needless to say i havnt bought 1 bottle of liquids from the shop since, all i get from the shops are my coils and they are fairly cheap ,
